i>Handling all issues regarding contracts</li>\r\n						</ul>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p><u>Candidate must:</u></p>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<ul>\r\n							<li>Have at least a high School Diploma</li>\r\n							<li>Maintain a clean, courteous and professional demeanor</li>\r\n							<li>Have a knowledge of computers, printers, and other office equipment</li>\r\n							<li>Have experience or training in secretarial work</li>\r\n							<li>Have attention to detail and high level of accuracy</li>\r\n							<li>Have effective time management and organizational skills</li>\r\n							<li>Be able to work independently and efficiently to meet deadlines</li>\r\n							<li>Have outstanding interpersonal and presentation skills</li>\r\n							<li>Be a licensed public notary</li>\r\n							<li>Have experience working with contracts</li>\r\n							<li>Paralegal preferred</li>\r\n						</ul>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p>\r\n						Benefits at Betop Corporation include dental, vision and health insurance, generous vacation and sick time, education and training, as well as a matching 401K program!\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p>\r\n					On email applications only, please submit a covering letter and CV, ensuring that the vacancy position applying for is included in the file and description of each \r\n					document uploaded. No Agencies.<br><br>The closing date for applications is 31th July at 4:00pm-CT. The interview/assessment date for this vacancy 16th August and will\r\n					be held at 931 S Kickapoo Ave. Springfield, MO</p><p>We want to make our application process as easy for you as we possibly can. If you have any more request please email us.</p>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>', '0000-00-00', 1),
